This paper is about a novel building block for image classification and dense prediction, which suggests that it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper proposes a new attention mechanism, which could fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also deals with segmentation, which could be classified under the natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-category. Finally, the paper evaluates its model on large-scale datasets, which could fall under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
